article.headline: Reaves scores 22, Iona takes down Vermont 62-59
article.description: — Dejour Reaves scored 22 points as Iona beat Vermont 62-59 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Reaves scores 22, Iona takes down Vermont 62-59
article.story: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y. -- — Dejour Reaves scored 22 points as Iona beat Vermont 62-59 on Friday night. Reaves added five rebounds and three steals for the Gaels (1-3). James Patterson scored 18 points while shooting 7 for 13 (2 for 6 from 3-point range) and 2 of 4 from the free-throw line and added six rebounds. TJ Long led the Catamounts (1-3) in scoring, finishing with 18 points and three steals. Vermont also got 16 points from TJ Hurley. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
